==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flip-flap
<hw>Flip"-flap`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Flip</er>, and <er>Flap</er>.]</ety> <def>The repeated stroke of
something long and loose.</def> <rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flip-flap</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Flip-flap
<hw>Flip"-flap`</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>With repeated strokes and
noise, as of something long and loose.</def> <rj><au>Ash.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flippancy</ent>⟦br⟧
